<h1 class="title">Socialism attempts to marry benefits of libertarianism with state power</h1>
<p>
Socialism attempts to marry the natural benefits of libertarianism &#x2013; freedom of scientific research, worker prosperity, and equality of opportunity &#x2013; with state power to bring about even greater good.  
</p>


